
    Pongola Regional Court convicted and sentenced five
accused to four life terms and a total of 225 years imprisonment for crimes
they committed at the local farms in March 2015.From December 2014 to March 2015, a group of armed men
would enter the farms in Pongola and Magudu policing precincts, rob the owners
of their valuables including firearms and rape the women.Cases were opened at Pongola and Magudu police stations. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjstiF-rALt7Ts4f99Oaw72XW7DWplUgUkrv7rXdEtvBWesdShbx27oC7FsiUWI4q2SLQpLdF0iuWSGRoxws8eOgtR2OFhIlSulzobyAEbjq3JcCfWgfPchAD2fgtJ9e4IKfU-ncISs6UvSgoEhKlQndLpjeQEOJ39tjSLaPFUqKg-_jBCEV5tsyV871UNxDs-Ni_sDRnsDg77J61I94wPi4TY4__Lxjft8NlcXyZptLRqtxUiK0Bc1mwotyZRCQwe-T6cvZMAeE_h922AlE0IZ_zp1_3zBs\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzAm_g5F2o5FYEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
